msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"Billing a call is the **action of setting a price** to a call that "
"implies cost."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:9
msgid "Billing calls depends upon an automatic process:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"When a call is about to be established, IvozProvider verifies that it "
"will be able to bill it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:13
msgid ""
"If with the current configuration (active and applicable rating plans for"
" a given client and for the specific destination) it won't be possible to"
" bill the call, IvozProvider will prevent its establishment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"Once a call that implies cost is hung up and is parsed by an asynchronous"
" process, it is listed in :ref:`external_calls`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:21
msgid "Billing methods"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"IvozProvider supports 3 different billing methods. Billing method is "
"configured at client level via *Billing method* parameter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:28
msgid "Postpaid billing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:30
#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:55
msgid "Call rating is done after the call ends."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:32
msgid "No configurable limit or balances involved."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:38
msgid "Prepaid billing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:40
msgid "Call rating is done during the call."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:42
msgid ""
"Clients with prepaid billing method have a preconfigured balance that "
"will be decrement during the call."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:44
msgid ""
"When the balance reaches zero, all established calls for the client will "
"hang up."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:46
msgid "Clients cannot place new calls with zero or negative balance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:48
#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:61
msgid "Low balance email notifications can be configured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:53
msgid "Pseudo-prepaid billing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:57
msgid ""
"Clients with pseudo-prepaid billing method have a preconfigured balance "
"that will be decrement after the call ends."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:59
msgid "Clients cannot place new calls with zero or below balance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:63
msgid ""
"Call duration is limited to the maximum duration possible with available "
"balance at the moment of call establishment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:67
msgid "Price and cost"
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:69
msgid ""
"Call **price** is the amount of money the brand operator will charge to "
"its **client** for every call."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:71
msgid ""
"Call **cost** is the amount of money the brand operator will be charged "
"by the **carrier** for every call."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:73
msgid ""
"**Call cost calculation is optional**, as no every carrier has *Calculate"
" Cost?* setting enabled. On the other hand, **call price calculation is "
"mandatory** for every outgoing call."
msgstr ""

#: ../../administration_portal/brand/billing/index.rst:76
msgid ""
"Carrier call cost calculation, if enabled, is always done postpaid. "
"Carriers with negative balance are allowed and no call will be hung up "
"when carrier balance reaches 0."
msgstr ""

